text:
{
  "prompt": "A stylish electric scooter with a pearl white body and metallic red accents. The scooter has a matte black seat and footrests, glossy black wheels and handlebars. Front and rear fenders are painted metallic red for a bold contrast. A very small and subtle silver lettering that reads 'doban' is placed discreetly near the bottom side panel. The overall design feels luxurious and refined, with a restrained yet artistic color composition. The background is neutral gray to keep focus on the vehicle.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A set of seven high-resolution electric scooters arranged side-by-side, each with a unique two-tone color scheme based on the colors of the rainbow. Each scooter has a clean and modern design, a minimalistic build with black seats and slim tires. Color combinations from left to right: 1) pearl white with metallic red, 2) cream ivory with candy orange, 3) light gray with sunshine yellow, 4) pearl silver with emerald green, 5) snow white with sky blue, 6) gray blue with midnight indigo, 7) matte black with pearl violet. The background is neutral gray to emphasize the scooter designs.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A digitally rendered side view of a sleek electric scooter with a slimmed-down battery compartment located beneath the footrest. The wheelbase is extended slightly for a more balanced and elongated profile. The scooter maintains a stylish and minimalist design with clean lines, black cushioned seat with backrest, modern wheels, and a subtle 'doban' logo on the side. The background is neutral gray to emphasize the streamlined modifications.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital image showcasing seven modern electric scooters in vibrant rainbow-inspired color schemes. Each scooter is presented in side view, set against a neutral gray background, and features a large 20-inch front wheel and a smaller 14-inch rear wheel. The frame design includes a slightly extended wheelbase and a slimmer battery housing under the step-through floorboard. The scooters are color-coded and labeled with names like 'Red Sunset', 'Orange Bloom', 'Yellow Point', 'Green Leaf', 'Blue Ocean', 'Indigo Deep', and 'Violet Mood'. Each has sleek black seating, minimalist handlebars, and a subtle 'doban' logo near the rear. The design balances style and practicality with clean contours and a modern urban aesthetic.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
